    "Github Copilot (https://github.com/features/copilot), along similar lines, also allows users to chat about their code base and receive code suggestions as outputs.",
    "It also includes a \"code completion\" feature.",
    "Startup coding products with similar capabilities include Source AI (https://sourceai.dev/), Replit AI (https://replit.com/ai), and Tabnine (https://www.tabnine.com/).",
    "Often, such products can help debug code too.",
    "Tools aimed specifically at teachers and students are more common in the creation space than in the discovery or understanding space."
  ],
